00:10:18.410 --> 00:10:19.661 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
So, um...

00:10:19.744 --> 00:10:21.204 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Yeah, what's up?

00:10:21.287 --> 00:10:23.623 position:50% align:center
