if I'm wrong.

00:10:29.045 --> 00:10:34.050 position:50% align:center
But, I kinda feel like,
I-I dunno.

00:10:34.134 --> 00:10:37.512 position:50% align:center
Maybe you might be interested
in cosplay after all?

00:10:38.263 --> 00:10:40.223 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA] When we were
at lunch the other day,

00:10:40.306 --> 00:10:41.933 position:50% align:center
