00:10:58.616 --> 00:10:59.951 position:50% align:center
There is one.

00:11:00.035 --> 00:11:02.037 position:50% align:center
A character that I love.

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:04.122 position:50% align:center
I thought maybe someday.

00:11:04.873 --> 00:11:06.708 position:50% align:center
