be a good fit at all.

00:11:21.598 --> 00:11:24.809 position:50% align:center
My sister might,
but I'm not cute like her,

00:11:24.893 --> 00:11:27.270 position:50% align:center
and my body type's all wrong.

00:11:27.354 --> 00:11:30.774 position:50% align:center
