horrible cosplay,

00:11:43.787 --> 00:11:46.164 position:50% align:center
I know I would
embarrass my sister.

00:11:46.247 --> 00:11:49.209 position:50% align:center
And I wouldn't be able
to handle it if she hated me.

00:11:49.292 --> 00:11:51.628 position:50% align:center
Plus, I'm too scared.

00:11:54.923 --> 00:11:56.800 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
That's confusing to me.

00:11:56.883 --> 00:11:58.385 position:50% align:center
When I was at the live event,

00:11:58.468 --> 00:12:02.806 position:50% align:center
I saw so many people enjoying
cosplay for the first time.

00:12:02.889 --> 00:12:05.975 position:50% align:center
And I remember thinking that
the best thing about cosplay

00:12:06.059 --> 00:12:08.603 position:50% align:center
is that you can
become anything you want.

00:12:10.355 --> 00:12:13.608 position:50% align:center
So I say, if you're
curious about it at all,

00:12:13.692 --> 00:12:15.276 position:50% align:center
you should try it!

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:18.697 position:50% align:center
And I'll help you!

00:12:18.780 --> 00:12:22.158 position:50% align:center
Also, I've seen how much
your sister loves you,

00:12:22.242 --> 00:12:25.245 position:50% align:center
and I don't think she
would ever judge you, Inui.

00:12:28.039 --> 00:12:29.374 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Thank you, Gojo.

00:12:29.457 --> 00:12:31.376 position:50% align:center
That means a lot.

00:12:31.459 --> 00:12:33.503 position:50% align:center
I would really
appreciate your help!

00:12:33.586 --> 00:12:36.214 position:50% align:center
Great! Then let's do it!

00:12:36.297 --> 00:12:38.717 position:50% align:center
So tell me, what series
do you want to cosplay from?

00:12:38.800 --> 00:12:40.677 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Actually, I hope you don't mind.

00:12:40.760 --> 00:12:44.264 position:50% align:center
My character is also from
<i>Flower Princess Blaze</i> !

00:12:44.347 --> 00:12:45.849 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Really? That's cool!

00:12:45.932 --> 00:12:47.517 position:50% align:center
I wonder which one it is.

00:12:47.600 --> 00:12:49.394 position:50% align:center
She said it was someone
totally different from her,

00:12:49.477 --> 00:12:51.438 position:50% align:center
so maybe it's
the heroine, Mirai.

00:12:51.521 --> 00:12:52.939 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Okay, don't laugh.

00:12:53.023 --> 00:12:55.233 position:50% align:center
I've always wanted
to try cosplaying Soma.

00:12:55.316 --> 00:12:57.360 position:50% align:center
Wait, you mean the brother?

00:12:57.444 --> 00:12:59.779 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU] I've always looked up
to him for so many reasons.

00:12:59.863 --> 00:13:01.156 position:50% align:center
He's strong, he's cool.

00:13:01.239 --> 00:13:03.408 position:50% align:center
And whenever his little sister,
Mirai is in trouble,

00:13:03.491 --> 00:13:06.578 position:50% align:center
he's the first one
to step up and help her.

00:13:06.661 --> 00:13:07.829 position:50% align:center
I think he's my favorite

00:13:07.912 --> 00:13:10.248 position:50% align:center
because he reminds me
so much of my sister.

00:13:10.331 --> 00:13:12.042 position:50% align:center
I see.

00:13:12.125 --> 00:13:14.210 position:50% align:center
You know, I bet you could be
part of the <i>Blaze</i> cosplay group

00:13:14.294 --> 00:13:15.462 position:50% align:center
with the others.

00:13:15.545 --> 00:13:17.088 position:50% align:center
I'm sure they'd both be
thrilled to have you.

00:13:17.172 --> 00:13:18.840 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Oh! That would be fun!

00:13:18.923 --> 00:13:21.426 position:50% align:center
But could you keep it
a secret until the day of?

00:13:21.509 --> 00:13:23.803 position:50% align:center
Since it's my first time,
I'm a little embarrassed.

00:13:23.887 --> 00:13:25.221 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Of course.

00:13:25.305 --> 00:13:28.224 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU] So, um, do you
really think I can pull it off?

00:13:28.308 --> 00:13:29.601 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Yeah, why not?

00:13:29.684 --> 00:13:33.229 position:50% align:center
Because I, um, I have
a hard time finding clothes

00:13:33.313 --> 00:13:35.190 position:50% align:center
that can fit me right on top.

00:13:35.273 --> 00:13:37.692 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA] Yeah, those might be
hard to work around.

00:13:37.776 --> 00:13:40.153 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Also, I only have my allowance,

00:13:40.236 --> 00:13:43.156 position:50% align:center
so I don't have
a lot of money to spend.

00:13:43.239 --> 00:13:44.324 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
That's right, I forgot!

00:13:44.407 --> 00:13:45.909 position:50% align:center
She's still in middle school!

00:13:45.992 --> 00:13:48.745 position:50% align:center
