I can do this for her.

00:14:03.051 --> 00:14:05.011 position:50% align:center
Think, dummy. Think!

00:14:05.095 --> 00:14:07.972 position:50% align:center
If that sounds too difficult,
please don't worry about it.

00:14:08.056 --> 00:14:09.391 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
No!

00:14:09.474 --> 00:14:12.060 position:50% align:center
I'll figure it out, don't worry!

00:14:16.147 --> 00:14:17.816 position:50% align:center
Let's start with
the outfit first.

00:14:17.899 --> 00:14:19.067 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Okay.

00:14:19.150 --> 00:14:21.444 position:50% align:center
