00:14:33.206 --> 00:14:35.208 position:50% align:center
You're sure it's okay
if I borrow it?

00:14:35.291 --> 00:14:38.169 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA] Yeah. I don't know
if it'll fit you as-is, but...

00:14:38.253 --> 00:14:39.504 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Let's see.

00:14:41.506 --> 00:14:42.507 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
It's a good thing Kitagawa

00:14:42.590 --> 00:14:45.301 position:50% align:center
