with hina dolls.

00:15:46.821 --> 00:15:49.866 position:50% align:center
Of course, they're all wearing
kimonos, so no buttons.

00:15:49.949 --> 00:15:52.744 position:50% align:center
Kimono! That's it!

00:15:52.827 --> 00:15:54.746 position:50% align:center
Let's try a <i>sarashi</i> wrap!

00:15:54.829 --> 00:15:56.539 position:50% align:center
We can use it to give you
a straighter shape.

00:15:56.623 --> 00:15:58.917 position:50% align:center
