of being a male character.

00:15:59.000 --> 00:16:00.335 position:50% align:center
What do you think, wanna try it?

00:16:00.418 --> 00:16:01.878 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Sounds good to me!

00:16:04.673 --> 00:16:05.757 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Now that I think of it,

00:16:05.840 --> 00:16:07.092 position:50% align:center
