00:16:14.391 --> 00:16:17.060 position:50% align:center
just for the sake of
looking like a character.

00:16:19.479 --> 00:16:20.480 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
But...

00:16:20.563 --> 00:16:22.232 position:50% align:center
[MARIN]
It's the ultimate form of love!

00:16:22.315 --> 00:16:26.027 position:50% align:center
