I want to be her!

00:16:26.111 --> 00:16:28.905 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
I think I understand why now.

00:16:28.988 --> 00:16:32.075 position:50% align:center
It's because they love
these characters so much.

00:16:43.086 --> 00:16:45.714 position:50% align:center
