00:17:13.408 --> 00:17:15.535 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU] What? It really
flattens it that much?

00:17:15.618 --> 00:17:17.328 position:50% align:center
Look, they have my size, too!

00:17:17.412 --> 00:17:20.290 position:50% align:center
