00:17:26.504 --> 00:17:27.630 position:50% align:center
Yay!

00:17:27.714 --> 00:17:29.883 position:50% align:center
I'll buy it right now!

00:17:29.966 --> 00:17:31.343 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
All that's left is the wig.

00:17:31.426 --> 00:17:33.261 position:50% align:center
