00:17:38.892 --> 00:17:40.226 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
'Kay, sit up straight.

00:17:40.310 --> 00:17:43.438 position:50% align:center
and keep looking forward.

00:17:47.650 --> 00:17:49.110 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA gasps]
I'm so sorry!

00:17:49.194 --> 00:17:50.862 position:50% align:center
I promise,
I didn't mean to do that!

00:17:50.945 --> 00:17:51.988 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
No, it's totally okay!

00:17:52.072 --> 00:17:54.491 position:50% align:center
I'm sorry!
Let's not talk about it!

00:17:57.369 --> 00:17:58.661 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Thanks for coming out here.

00:17:58.745 --> 00:18:00.205 position:50% align:center
I know it's a bit
of a hike for you.

00:18:00.288 --> 00:18:01.581 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
I don't mind!

00:18:01.664 --> 00:18:04.000 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Come look, I got your wig!

00:18:04.084 --> 00:18:06.336 position:50% align:center
Since you want your cosplay
to be a surprise,

00:18:06.419 --> 00:18:08.380 position:50% align:center
