cut it ourselves.

00:18:12.592 --> 00:18:13.927 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Wow.

00:18:14.010 --> 00:18:16.680 position:50% align:center
He's never cut a wig,
and he's not hesitating at all.

00:18:31.778 --> 00:18:32.904 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Uh...

00:18:32.987 --> 00:18:34.447 position:50% align:center
Heh...

00:18:34.531 --> 00:18:36.199 position:50% align:center
It's kinda nerve-racking.

00:18:36.282 --> 00:18:37.992 position:50% align:center
Ohh...

00:18:38.076 --> 00:18:39.494 position:50% align:center
[chuckles]

00:18:39.577 --> 00:18:42.038 position:50% align:center
I'm freaking out a little bit;
I don't wanna mess it up.

00:18:42.122 --> 00:18:43.873 position:50% align:center
--[SHINJU] Hah.
--Huh?

00:18:43.957 --> 00:18:45.792 position:50% align:center
No! It's fine!

00:18:45.875 --> 00:18:48.878 position:50% align:center
I'm just so relieved that you
feel that way sometimes, too.

00:18:48.962 --> 00:18:50.588 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
I-I definitely do!

00:18:50.672 --> 00:18:52.882 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU] But you make
the most incredible outfits!

00:18:52.966 --> 00:18:55.677 position:50% align:center
How could someone so
talented ever be insecure?

00:18:55.760 --> 00:18:56.636 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Are you kidding?

00:18:56.720 --> 00:18:58.221 position:50% align:center
There's so much I can't do!

00:18:58.304 --> 00:18:59.889 position:50% align:center
I'm still trying
to figure it all out!

00:18:59.973 --> 00:19:01.641 position:50% align:center
Do you really mean that?

00:19:04.602 --> 00:19:05.395 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Yeah.

00:19:05.478 --> 00:19:06.646 position:50% align:center
I actually wish I could be more

00:19:06.730 --> 00:19:08.732 position:50% align:center
like this classmate
I look up to.

00:19:08.815 --> 00:19:10.608 position:50% align:center
She's always so positive.

00:19:10.692 --> 00:19:12.861 position:50% align:center
Everyone who meets
her loves her.

00:19:12.944 --> 00:19:15.989 position:50% align:center
She's strong, and fearless, and
says whatever is on her mind.

00:19:16.072 --> 00:19:18.491 position:50% align:center
I always thought
her life must be so easy.

00:19:18.575 --> 00:19:21.202 position:50% align:center
There was no way she
had problems like me.

00:19:21.286 --> 00:19:24.581 position:50% align:center
But then,
one thing lead to another,

00:19:24.664 --> 00:19:26.708 position:50% align:center
and I ended up spending
a lot of time with her,

00:19:26.791 --> 00:19:28.960 position:50% align:center
and I realized...

00:19:29.044 --> 00:19:32.047 position:50% align:center
...she also had things she
wanted to do but couldn't.

00:19:32.130 --> 00:19:34.341 position:50% align:center
And things didn't
always go her way.

00:19:34.424 --> 00:19:36.384 position:50% align:center
She even messed up at times.

00:19:36.468 --> 00:19:39.471 position:50% align:center
She has the same issues I do.

00:19:39.554 --> 00:19:43.433 position:50% align:center
But she always looks happy.

00:19:43.516 --> 00:19:46.269 position:50% align:center
And sometimes
she's even kinda cute.

00:19:46.353 --> 00:19:47.312 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:19:47.395 --> 00:19:48.897 position:50% align:center
Hold on! Did I say cute?

00:19:48.980 --> 00:19:51.024 position:50% align:center
If-If I did, I swear,
I didn't mean it like that!

00:19:51.107 --> 00:19:52.734 position:50% align:center
Anyway. What?

00:19:52.817 --> 00:19:53.777 position:50% align:center
Did you say something?

00:19:53.860 --> 00:19:55.653 position:50% align:center
I forgot what
I was talking about.

00:19:55.737 --> 00:19:56.946 position:50% align:center
Oh, yeah.

00:19:58.198 --> 00:19:59.532 position:50% align:center
My point was,

00:19:59.616 --> 00:20:01.826 position:50% align:center
we don't always know
how someone really feels.

00:20:01.910 --> 00:20:05.205 position:50% align:center
But, well,
we all have struggles.

00:20:05.288 --> 00:20:07.499 position:50% align:center
Anyway. Haircuts!

00:20:10.752 --> 00:20:14.339 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
We all have struggles. Even her?

00:20:15.256 --> 00:20:17.425 position:50% align:center
I never thought
about it that way.

00:20:17.509 --> 00:20:19.678 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
Okay, let's do your makeup!

00:20:19.761 --> 00:20:21.805 position:50% align:center
I found everything you need
at the hundred-yen shop.

00:20:21.888 --> 00:20:24.724 position:50% align:center
I got this entire bag
for under ten thousand!

00:20:24.808 --> 00:20:27.602 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Wow! Thank you so much!

00:20:30.230 --> 00:20:32.816 position:50% align:center
Looks good,
let's do your eyes next.

00:20:32.899 --> 00:20:34.859 position:50% align:center
To make your eyes look
a little more masculine,

00:20:34.943 --> 00:20:37.320 position:50% align:center
we'll extend the eyeliner
a bit further than normal.

00:20:37.404 --> 00:20:39.531 position:50% align:center
And the last thing we'll
do is adjust the wig.

00:20:39.614 --> 00:20:42.325 position:50% align:center
Oh! There he is!

00:20:43.952 --> 00:20:48.707 position:50% align:center
[JUJU]
No. Shinju?

00:20:48.790 --> 00:20:55.255 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU] Hi. Um, I, um,
I wanted to, I guess...

00:20:55.338 --> 00:20:59.592 position:50% align:center
Just try...
sorta try cosplaying.

00:21:01.344 --> 00:21:04.723 position:50% align:center
No way. I just... I can't
believe it. You look amazing!

00:21:04.806 --> 00:21:06.850 position:50% align:center
Omigosh! What she said!

00:21:06.933 --> 00:21:08.518 position:50% align:center
I couldn't
tell who you were at first.

00:21:08.601 --> 00:21:13.398 position:50% align:center
[MARIN, JUJU
clamoring with excitement]

00:21:14.649 --> 00:21:17.027 position:50% align:center
Just so good. I mean it.

00:21:17.110 --> 00:21:20.780 position:50% align:center
Perfect. I'm so impressed!

00:21:24.617 --> 00:21:26.745 position:50% align:center
Do you like it?

00:21:30.415 --> 00:21:31.791 position:50% align:center
Yes.

00:21:31.875 --> 00:21:32.959 position:50% align:center
So, question.

00:21:33.043 --> 00:21:34.878 position:50% align:center
What'd you do with your yabbos?

00:21:34.961 --> 00:21:36.004 position:50% align:center
They're like MIA!

00:21:36.087 --> 00:21:37.464 position:50% align:center
I strapped them down

00:21:37.547 --> 00:21:39.132 position:50% align:center
with a compression band
and a <i>sarashi</i> wrap.

00:21:39.215 --> 00:21:41.593 position:50% align:center
Then Gojo sewed in
some shoulder pads for me!

00:21:41.676 --> 00:21:43.553 position:50% align:center
You still have a girl face!

00:21:43.762 --> 00:21:45.013 position:50% align:center
Girl face?

00:21:45.096 --> 00:21:46.848 position:50% align:center
You've got like this
powerful presence of a dude,

00:21:46.931 --> 00:21:48.892 position:50% align:center
but your face still
looks so girly,

00:21:48.975 --> 00:21:52.062 position:50% align:center
the contrast is so cool,
and I seriously can't with you!

00:21:52.145 --> 00:21:54.689 position:50% align:center
Omigosh, Shinju, can we
take a few selfies together?

00:21:54.773 --> 00:21:56.483 position:50% align:center
Pretty please!

00:22:00.111 --> 00:22:01.404 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Sure!

00:22:02.489 --> 00:22:04.157 position:50% align:center
[MARIN]
Okay, cute. One more!

00:22:04.240 --> 00:22:05.283 position:50% align:center
And this time.

00:22:05.367 --> 00:22:06.076 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA] I think we
should get started

00:22:06.159 --> 00:22:06.951 position:50% align:center
before our time runs out.

00:22:07.035 --> 00:22:08.078 position:50% align:center
[JUJU]
Oh, that's right!

00:22:08.161 --> 00:22:09.329 position:50% align:center
I forgot we're paying hourly!

00:22:09.412 --> 00:22:10.872 position:50% align:center
Shinju, can you get the camera?

00:22:10.955 --> 00:22:12.332 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
Yep! On it!

00:22:12.415 --> 00:22:13.458 position:50% align:center
[EVERYONE screams]

00:22:13.541 --> 00:22:15.960 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA]
That camera is really not cheap!

00:22:16.044 --> 00:22:17.629 position:50% align:center
[SHINJU]
It's fine, you guys.

00:23:47.594 --> 00:23:48.887 position:50% align:center
[MARIN, SHINJU, JUJU]
Next time.